<br />
Mana:  	700  	Skill:  	Alteration
<br />
Casting Time: 	5 	Recast Time: 	2.25
<br />
Fizzle Time: 	2.25 	Resist: 	Magic
<br />
Range: 	200 	
<br />

<br />
700 mana = ouch. Also cast time is significantly longer than bard charm, and they can't cast on the move. Recast time also favors the bard in case of resist. The L64 PoP mezz costs 300 mana, casts in 2.5, has a -10 resist mod, and has the same recast. </span></td>
